title: BigFish Games - Emergency Hospital FINAL - New Dash [h33t][Wendy
description:
Emergency Hospital is an exciting and whimsical new time management 
game with brilliant graphics and challenging gameplay. Play as you run 
a successful hospital by diagnosing and treating patients. The game 
features two different game play modes, and seven diverse, customizable 
locations. Treat hundreds of unique types of patients suffering from 
different ailments and conditions. Enjoy hours of hospital humor, and 
faced-paced fun.

Thanx to TAC-CM
